Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.47,0:00:03.73,Signs_EpTitle,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(531,519)\pos(173.5,22)}Episode 9\N\N\NPlanetary Gravity
Dialogue: 1,0:00:01.73,0:00:04.73,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,By the way, are you the leader \Nof this team, Raimon-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.73,0:00:06.39,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,It's Umi-chairwoman!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.39,0:00:07.86,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,So it's you, Konohoshi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.86,0:00:09.86,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,Here's to good luck for both our speeches!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.16,0:00:13.40,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,I'll be looking forward to \Nyour rocket presentation!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.37,0:00:19.75,Default,Akane,0,0,0,,Barging into enemy territory \Nall by her lonesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.75,0:00:22.35,Default,Akane,0,0,0,,Is she that confident as reigning champion?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.66,0:00:27.88,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(489,1)\alpha&H33&\an7\bord0\blur0.2\pos(20,20)\p1\c&HFDFFFD&\fscx233\fscy155}m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100
