Dialogue: 1,0:00:23.66,0:00:27.88,Signs_Boxed,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(489,1)\an7\fs10\c&H5E4C3B&\pos(76.5,47.5)\3c&HCDCF72&\bord1.5}\hEvents\h\N\N{\bord0\fs8}Start of reception\NLicense checks and inspection of engines used\NIgniter installation lecture, launch order lottery\NDistribution of raw eggs\NStart of first launch round in designated order\NEnd of first launch round\NRetrieval of rockets\NRecess (lunch break)\NStart of second launch round\NEnd of second launch round\NRetrieval of rockets\NAward ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.21,0:00:30.09,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,That's why our team wanted to try \Nsome different ideas this year,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.09,0:00:33.25,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,and after using our department's shared \N3D CAD license to create a model,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.25,0:00:36.39,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,we borrowed the architectural \Ndesign department's 3D printer
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:38.39,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,to make streamlined fins.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.67,0:00:43.39,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,Ah, my advisor told me to include that part \Nto serve as advertisement for our school!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.16,0:00:47.38,Default,Matataki,0,0,0,,She's laughing away like an idiot, as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.38,0:00:50.48,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,She's very good at winning over the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.48,0:00:51.40,Default,Matataki,0,0,0,,Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.59,0:00:58.93,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,Umika, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.57,0:01:04.34,DefaultItalics,Announcer,0,0,0,,And now for Tatsuoka High School of \NScience and Technology's first launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.42,0:01:13.92,DefaultItalics,Announcer,0,0,0,,Off it goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.77,0:01:19.82,DefaultItalics,Announcer,0,0,0,,The parachute has deployed!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.35,0:01:32.57,DefaultItalics,Announcer,0,0,0,,The payload has been successfully recovered!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.93,0:01:34.82,DefaultItalics,Announcer,0,0,0,,The egg is unharmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.40,0:01:39.74,DefaultItalics,Announcer,0,0,0,,The results are in!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.11,0:01:42.65,DefaultItalics,Announcer,0,0,0,,Attained altitude: 809 feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.65,0:01:45.82,DefaultItalics,Announcer,0,0,0,,Airborne time: 48.84 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.82,0:01:48.75,DefaultItalics,Announcer,0,0,0,,A score of 32.36!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.75,0:01:51.18,DefaultItalics,Announcer,0,0,0,,They're currently first place \Nin the qualifying round!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.18,0:01:53.46,Default,Matataki,0,0,0,,They basically hit all the target values.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.46,0:01:54.53,Default,Matataki,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.53,0:01:56.01,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,Oh, my apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:01:59.76,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,There's something I forgot to \Nmention in my earlier speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.76,0:02:02.95,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,To account for the wind today, \Nas well as atmospheric pressure,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.95,0:02:06.08,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,we had made adjustments to our rocket's \Nweight and the center of gravity,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.08,0:02:10.02,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,and as a bit of an experiment, \Nwe attached a miniature camera on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.30,0:02:14.15,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,We'll be uploading the aerial \Nfootage online afterwards,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.15,0:02:16.02,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,so please feel free to take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.38,0:02:19.73,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,That's all I have! Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.90,0:02:23.96,Default,Official,0,0,0,,Fujinomisaki High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.96,0:02:26.28,Default,Official,0,0,0,,Please get ready for your launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.28,0:02:28.34,Default,Official,0,0,0,,If your representative could follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.19,0:02:30.32,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Umika-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.94,0:02:34.42,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,Akizuki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.84,0:02:37.59,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,She really was so awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.15,0:02:42.58,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,So confident, even when speaking \Nin front of so many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.58,0:02:46.06,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,Intellectual, but with a sense of humor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.23,0:02:51.02,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,She ended up making a perfect rocket, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.03,0:02:54.62,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,I need to be perfect as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.62,0:02:56.61,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,Umika, are you gonna be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.82,0:02:59.05,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:03.41,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,I'm fine. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.57,0:03:08.95,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,All the other times... \Nit ended up being fine in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.77,0:03:12.52,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,The time we faced off against Raimon-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:16.21,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,When I presented alone at \Nthe club presidents meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.02,0:03:21.22,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,So I'm sure this time will be no different.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:23.24,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,As chairwoman...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.91,0:03:25.72,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,Like Akizuki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.38,0:03:27.72,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,I can do it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.73,0:03:33.92,Narration,Umika,0,0,0,,The moment I set foot on \Nthe podium, legs trembling,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.55,0:03:37.48,Narration,Umika,0,0,0,,I realized it in a moment of clarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:42.39,Narration,Umika,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.01,0:03:47.74,Narration,Umika,0,0,0,,I could never be Akizuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.72,0:03:55.97,Narration,Umika,0,0,0,,From everyone's reactions, I could tell \Nthat my speech hadn't gone well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.97,0:03:59.21,Narration,Umika,0,0,0,,Even so, Takaragi-san gave me \Nwords of encouragement,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:02.14,Narration,Umika,0,0,0,,and Akeuchi-san lightened the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.73,0:04:06.86,Narration,Umika,0,0,0,,My jittery hands weren't able \Nto set up the rocket very well,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.86,0:04:10.02,Narration,Umika,0,0,0,,so Raimon-san was kind \Nenough to fix it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:11.90,Narration,Umika,0,0,0,,As for our rocket...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.90,0:04:16.92,Narration,Umika,0,0,0,,Our first attempt got no mark, thanks to a \Nmisfire caused by an igniter contact failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.92,0:04:21.74,Narration,Umika,0,0,0,,Our second attempt resulted in a launch, \Nbut we greatly overshot the target altitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:25.35,Narration,Umika,0,0,0,,Consequently, the Rocket Research Hobby Group
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:28.88,Narration,Umika,0,0,0,,did not advance past the qualifying round.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.93,0:04:36.38,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,We're pretty much done gathering everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.69,0:04:41.20,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Sensei said she'd carry all of \Nthe heavy luggage to the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:48.91,Default,Matataki,0,0,0,,Looks like it's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.07,0:04:53.14,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Matataki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.59,0:04:56.38,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,Ah, Raimon-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:04:59.23,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,Good job on the launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:01.90,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,Ah, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:04.03,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\blur0.2\fnComic Sans MS\c&H183F66&\b0\frz16.28\fax-0.35\fscx80\move(239.5,151.5,253,175,110,402)}For the grilled corn\NThanks
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.23,0:05:04.03,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,This is, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.03,0:05:05.10,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.10,0:05:09.03,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,I figured I should just pay you back today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:14.54,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Matataki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:16.82,Default,Haruno,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.95,0:05:19.89,Default,Matataki,0,0,0,,Must be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.89,0:05:23.33,Default,Matataki,0,0,0,,You don't care whether we win or lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:26.14,Default,Matataki,0,0,0,,Even without this group—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.14,0:05:31.26,Default,Matataki,0,0,0,,no matter who you're with, \Nit's all the same to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:38.02,Default,Matataki,0,0,0,,This was the only place where I belonged.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.88,0:05:42.02,Default,Matataki,0,0,0,,Don't you ever talk to me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.99,0:05:53.24,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I-I can take all the small things \Nback w-with me by bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:56.54,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,So I guess w-we're done for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.84,0:06:03.05,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,A-Akeuchi-san, take S-Sensei's car \Nback home and rest up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:05.46,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,Umika, are you having a hard time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.09,0:06:07.83,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,I don't need to make contact to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:10.72,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,On the long journey toward our dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:13.31,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,there's bound to be a misstep \Nor two along the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:14.47,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:16.31,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,We've only just begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:19.02,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,Next time, we'll make an even better rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:19.77,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:21.40,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,With everyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.33,0:06:23.48,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:24.07,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:27.50,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.96,0:06:32.53,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I can't speak well like Akizuki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.53,0:06:35.08,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I can't be a charismatic leader like her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:36.83,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,It was the same with making the rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:40.12,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I was nothing but a useless \Nburden to the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:44.21,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,We all started this group, but I can't \Nget it promoted to a full-fledged club!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:46.10,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.75,0:06:48.97,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I can't do any of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:52.70,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,And when it comes to helping you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.70,0:06:53.99,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.99,0:06:58.43,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I can't take you into outer space.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:00.10,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:01.32,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,Umika!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.38,0:07:12.65,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,Huh? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:17.12,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,I can't see the sparkles anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.45,0:07:25.63,Narration,Umika,0,0,0,,A big dream that shines brilliantly \Nwith every step forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.01,0:07:27.57,Narration,Umika,0,0,0,,Together with everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.57,0:07:30.66,Narration,Umika,0,0,0,,as it grows without end in size... \Nand in brilliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.63,0:07:35.89,Narration,Umika,0,0,0,,However, I was the one who ruined it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.72,0:07:38.64,Narration,Umika,0,0,0,,If this is how it ends...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.13,0:07:42.64,Narration,Umika,0,0,0,,I would have been better off \Nbeing all alone from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.60,0:07:50.53,Default,Honami,0,0,0,,Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:08:00.04,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fnTimes New Roman\bord2\c&H647282&\3c&HCAFFF9&\fs18}Fabric Softener Refill\N{\fs12}Shockingly effective!\N{\fs16}Deodorizer / Antibacterial
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.85,0:08:00.04,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,The groceries Hona asked me to get...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:02.54,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,Was this all of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:06.54,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(235,1)\fnTimes New Roman\c&H453E33&\pos(327.5,222)}Alien
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:06.54,Flashback,Honami,0,0,0,,Go get some fresh air, instead of \Nbeing cooped up in your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.54,0:08:09.80,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,Was it always this hot out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:13.80,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,I'd forgotten, from being \Nin my room for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.69,0:08:17.49,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,If only it'd all been a dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.84,0:08:22.81,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,If only the second term would never start...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.74,0:08:24.63,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.28,0:08:27.81,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,Konohoshi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.81,0:08:30.07,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,How have you been the past week?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:37.45,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,It sure is hot out today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.92,0:08:41.23,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,We haven't had a chance to \Ntalk since the championship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.23,0:08:43.15,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,I just couldn't help but say hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.15,0:08:44.08,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.15,0:08:50.36,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,It had a fine launch—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.36,0:08:52.17,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,the rocket that your team made.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:08:57.04,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,It really was a fine launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.02,0:09:05.77,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,I know you might not take this \Nso well coming from me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.77,0:09:10.30,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,but when I saw your rocket \Nsoar straight up like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.30,0:09:12.53,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,it felt like a breath of fresh air.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.64,0:09:16.77,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,The weather conditions \Nweren't great that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.77,0:09:20.52,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,But that clean, powerful trajectory, \Nreaching high into the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.52,0:09:22.91,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,It really was exhilarating!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.26,0:09:29.54,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,So I wanted to share that excitement I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:33.40,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,It was thanks to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.40,0:09:37.55,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,The whole group worked hard \Nto launch that rocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:40.98,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,Yeah, including you as the leader—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:41.68,DefaultTop,Umika,0,0,0,,Y-You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.36,0:09:48.44,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,A-All I did was t-tell everyone \NI wanted to build a rocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:50.64,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I d-didn't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:52.26,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.26,0:09:56.45,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I'm... no leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.07,0:09:59.43,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:05.17,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,If you don't mind, can you tell me about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.31,0:10:11.08,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,The spark that made you first \Nwant to build a rocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:14.52,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,What was it that drove you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.84,0:10:22.21,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,You wanted to go to space to find \Nfriends that your words would reach?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.21,0:10:24.35,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,What a fascinating idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:29.53,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,It's absurd to think there {\i1}wouldn't{\i0} be life \Nout in the vast reaches of space!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.53,0:10:34.00,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,Which means that your plan \Nis teeming with potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.00,0:10:38.52,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,And there's something really inspiring \Nabout finding a place where you belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.52,0:10:40.11,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,I think it's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.49,0:10:44.70,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,A-Akizuki-san, you're too kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:51.28,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,A-Anyone else would laugh \Nat a dream like mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.28,0:10:53.16,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,Since I can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.16,0:10:56.25,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,All I do is talk big.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:10:59.69,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I'll n-never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:01.01,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I can't change anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:04.83,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I'll always be weak and helpless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:09.10,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I know that I'll never \Nactually make it anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.10,0:11:14.02,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I know that I don't belong anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.37,0:11:20.95,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,But Takaragi-san, Raimon-san, \Nand Akeuchi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:23.85,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,None of them laughed at your dream, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:24.66,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.67,0:11:31.65,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,They thought your dream sounded \Nexciting, so they joined you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.65,0:11:34.89,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,They wanted to become a part \Nof that dream of yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.89,0:11:37.38,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,so they built a rocket with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:41.72,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,They believed in your dream, \Nso they chose you to be the leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:45.65,Flashback,Haruno,0,0,0,,You're all trying to go to outer space?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.65,0:11:47.13,Flashback,Haruno,0,0,0,,Sounds like a lot of fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.13,0:11:49.71,Flashback,Matataki,0,0,0,,Nothing wrong with outer space, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.71,0:11:51.82,Flashback,Matataki,0,0,0,,If that's how you really feel, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.82,0:11:54.85,Flashback,Yu,0,0,0,,I think your dream is really awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.82,0:12:00.71,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,You know, Konohoshi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.30,0:12:05.57,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,There might be a place where you belong \Nright here on this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.31,0:12:10.41,Flashback,Matataki,0,0,0,,Weren't you looking for a place to belong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.93,0:12:13.46,Flashback,Matataki,0,0,0,,Now you have one, so good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:18.59,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,Have you never stopped \Nto think about it that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.43,0:12:20.85,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.85,0:12:28.28,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,B-B-But I was the one who r-r-ruined it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.28,0:12:32.23,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,In that case, you just have to \Nfind some firm footing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.67,0:12:37.86,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,Just like how a rocket pushes off \Nthe firm ground into the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:41.44,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,we humans can't fly high \Nwith shaky footing, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:46.74,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,Solid footing is what will allow you \Nto soar further and higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.09,0:12:51.24,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,Consider yourself lucky if you fall over \Nand discover a weak spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.92,0:12:54.50,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,That just means you can make it \Nsturdier for next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:59.34,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,So don't just blindly blame \Nyourself for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:01.40,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,You need to fully understand:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.40,0:13:03.63,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,what is it that you have now,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.63,0:13:05.38,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,and what is it that you lack?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.07,0:13:10.09,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,Hey, are you going to stay down?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.09,0:13:12.88,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,Are you just going to give up on it all?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.88,0:13:16.20,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,Even though you have room to stand back up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.20,0:13:18.95,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,Are you just going to turn a blind eye to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.06,0:13:22.79,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,The... The...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.79,0:13:24.97,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,The place where I belong...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.27,0:13:30.53,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,I was always scared that \NI didn't belong anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:35.83,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,I wasn't proud at all about \Nwhere I currently was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.13,0:13:39.51,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,All I wanted was to look up \Nand yearn for the distant stars—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.04,0:13:42.69,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,the farther, the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.69,0:13:46.68,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,That way, I could look away from \Nthe darkness at my own feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:51.51,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,But if I have a place here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:53.96,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,If it's okay for me to be here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.96,0:13:57.60,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,If I want to stay here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.51,0:14:02.91,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I want to get up and see for myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.00,0:14:06.64,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,what I can do right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:11.84,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,Now that I realize... that everyone \Nhas made a place for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.84,0:14:15.33,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,Now that I want to take good care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.94,0:14:18.22,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,Even if I make a fool of myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.22,0:14:24.09,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I want to stand tall, so that \NI might take flight someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.74,0:14:27.93,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,Feel free to reach out at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.60,0:14:30.09,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.41,0:14:35.47,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,U-Um, g-good luck at the \Nnational championship!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:37.20,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:40.23,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, about the tournament...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.23,0:14:46.92,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,There's a good number of past entrants who \Nare now working in the aerospace industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.92,0:14:49.81,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,The experience of launching \Nyour very own rocket
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.81,0:14:53.12,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,has inspired a lot of people \Nto go down that path.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:58.75,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,And you know, with good results, you can \Nuse it for recommendation into a university!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.13,0:15:02.26,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,So as a stepping stone for \Nmaking it to outer space,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.26,0:15:08.63,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,taking part in model rocketry as a high \Nschooler makes sense on a practical level,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.63,0:15:10.01,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,a-and, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:10.86,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.70,0:15:16.01,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,I look forward to facing off \Nagainst you all next year!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:21.35,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I'll ask everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:26.65,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,a-and talk about our plans going forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:29.53,Default,Kei,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.95,0:15:36.28,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,Akizuki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.55,0:15:37.78,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.66,0:15:41.52,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,I need to tell everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.07,0:15:44.98,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,and apologize to Akeuchi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.06,0:15:52.02,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,Akeuchi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.63,0:15:55.39,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,Is she not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.55,0:15:59.56,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnArial Black\c&H8942D7&\3c&HF0DBFF&\bord1\frz-51.06\fax-0.17\pos(375,139.5)}I'm inside!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.55,0:15:59.56,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fs16\fscx90\fnComic Sans MS\c&H465063&\3c&HBCCFE3&\frz-51.06\fax-0.17\pos(434,216)}Come hang out
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.88,0:15:59.14,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I'll... wait here a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.92,0:16:05.44,DefaultItalicsTop,Ringtone,0,0,0,,UFO! UFO! Emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:07.85,DefaultItalicsTop,Ringtone,0,0,0,,UFO! UFO! Abduction!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.85,0:16:08.97,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I fell asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.85,0:16:10.57,DefaultItalicsTop,Ringtone,0,0,0,,UFO! UFO! Emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.57,0:16:11.43,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.43,0:16:12.67,DefaultItalics,Honami,0,0,0,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.67,0:16:13.51,DefaultItalics,Honami,0,0,0,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.51,0:16:15.20,DefaultItalics,Honami,0,0,0,,Are you safe? Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.20,0:16:15.92,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.92,0:16:17.26,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I'm at a friend's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.26,0:16:18.45,DefaultItalics,Honami,0,0,0,,A friend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.45,0:16:20.95,DefaultItalicsTop,Umika,0,0,0,,Wh-When did it get so late?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:23.96,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(318,1)\blur0.25\fs8\an7\c&H7C6E3E&\frz-8.37\fax-0.03\pos(299.67,153.67)}Honami\N\N{\b0}Missed call\N\N{\c&HD1CBC5&}5 more missed calls
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:23.96,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(318,1)\blur0.25\fs8\an9\c&HD1CBC5&\fax-0.03\b0\frz352.2\pos(424.683,179.157)}4 minutes ago
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:23.96,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(318,1)\blur0.25\fs8\an7\c&H7C6E3E&\frz-8.37\fax-0.03\pos(289.67,214.34)}Honami\N\N{\b0}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:23.96,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(318,1)\blur0.25\fs8\an9\c&HE4D4BD&\fax-0.03\b0\frz352.2\pos(414.683,240.824)}3 hours ago
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:23.96,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(318,1)\blur0.25\fs8\an7\c&H7C6E3E&\frz-8.37\fax-0.03\pos(282.337,255.337)}Honami\N\N{\b0}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:23.96,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(318,1)\blur0.25\fs8\an9\c&HE4D4BD&\fax-0.03\b0\frz352.2\pos(409.016,282.491)}3 hours ago
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:23.96,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(318,1)\blur0.25\fs8\an7\c&H7C6E3E&\frz-8.37\fax-0.03\pos(274.337,295.337)}Honami
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:23.96,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(318,1)\blur0.25\fs8\an7\fscx90\c&H7C6E3E&\frz-8.37\fax-0.03\pos(227.51,311.25)\b0}Were you able to buy fabric softener? If they're out, that's fine.
