Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.95,0:16:22.76,DefaultItalicsTop,Umika's Mother,0,0,0,,L-Let's call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.76,0:16:23.96,DefaultItalicsTop,Honami,0,0,0,,Mom, hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.96,0:16:26.58,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I-I'm perfectly fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.58,0:16:27.85,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,Yeah, I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.85,0:16:29.79,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I-I'm sleeping over, for my club.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.79,0:16:31.01,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.01,0:16:31.73,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.73,0:16:33.34,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I-I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:34.70,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,Yes, I'll call again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:35.97,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:40.68,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,Is Akeuchi-san still out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.62,0:16:43.10,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,Akeuchi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:44.69,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.46,0:16:50.32,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,Huh? The lights aren't coming on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.96,0:16:53.07,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,Is there a lantern around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.69,0:16:57.15,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,The voyage log...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.15,0:16:59.45,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,This is where it always was.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.87,0:17:02.26,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,I don't see any of her \Nother belongings, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:07.52,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,The basement key...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.52,0:17:09.46,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,What's it doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.75,0:17:14.09,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,Akeuchi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.38,0:17:21.20,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,The basement was completely empty, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.20,0:17:26.72,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,It's like every trace of Akeuchi-san \Ndisappeared from the lighthouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.60,0:17:30.49,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,Did she go off somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.67,0:17:33.67,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,No, that can't be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.67,0:17:39.62,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,She wouldn't be out so late, \Nwith all of her belongings in hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.07,0:17:45.62,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,She must have packed up and left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.06,0:17:49.17,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,Because of the terrible way I treated her,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:52.72,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,Akeuchi-san's gone and left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:18:00.34,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,Just when I'd finally realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.34,0:18:06.06,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,A-After I'd decided \Nto protect the place I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.06,0:18:07.09,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,All of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.09,0:18:09.87,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,All of it was... was too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.10,0:18:12.94,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:15.40,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I don't want this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.40,0:18:16.39,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:21.83,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,H-Having the last words \NI said to her be so awful...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:23.77,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I don't want that at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.42,0:18:29.02,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I-I want to talk to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.02,0:18:32.80,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I-I want one more chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:38.68,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,Akeuchi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:42.78,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,Akeuchi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:47.51,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,Akeuchi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:54.11,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,Umika.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.02,0:19:02.12,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,Did you call for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:08.21,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.21,0:19:09.21,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.21,0:19:09.97,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.97,0:19:14.63,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I said those terrible things, \Nabout not being able to go to space.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:18.63,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,A-After I promised \Nto take you there one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:22.61,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,After our promise to go together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.61,0:19:23.62,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:24.72,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.82,0:19:26.83,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,Umika.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.41,0:19:28.64,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:31.39,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,I understand everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.39,0:19:35.15,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,So please don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.24,0:19:41.41,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for making you \Nbear the burden alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.15,0:19:47.02,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I-Is it really okay for me to stay the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.02,0:19:48.13,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,You betcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.13,0:19:51.11,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,Isn't that what you told your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.11,0:19:56.42,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,Besides, it's my fault \Nfor staying out so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:59.55,DefaultItalics,Umika,0,0,0,,So she hadn't left for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:02.37,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,Looks like I made you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.37,0:20:04.28,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,No, I'm just glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.28,0:20:08.56,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I-I have a lot of things \NI wanted to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.98,0:20:13.06,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,In that case, the lighthouse at night \Nis the perfect place to relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.53,0:20:17.82,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,I want to hear everything \Nyou have to say, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.99,0:20:21.33,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,Akeuchi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.38,0:20:24.11,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.11,0:20:25.82,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,I really should ask first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:30.80,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,Even after I upset you last time, \NI did it again...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.02,0:20:32.83,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.83,0:20:37.09,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,B-Back then, I avoided your foreheadpathy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.09,0:20:41.22,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,because I-I couldn't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.22,0:20:46.55,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,Not you, not anyone else, and not even me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.55,0:20:52.23,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I h-had convinced myself that I needed \Nto solve everything without anyone's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.57,0:20:55.52,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,You see, I understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.52,0:21:00.73,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,That there's a place where I belong, \Nh-here on this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.73,0:21:05.57,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I-I might keep messing up again, like before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.57,0:21:08.49,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I might make a fool of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.93,0:21:13.71,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,But even so, I want to \Nprotect this place—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.06,0:21:18.63,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,th-the Rocket Research Hobby \NGroup that we all started.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.63,0:21:21.71,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I want to take flight here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.71,0:21:25.22,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,Together with everyone—with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.74,0:21:26.97,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,Umika.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.04,0:21:29.85,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,What a warm light.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.85,0:21:32.35,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,It'd never disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.35,0:21:33.97,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,Right here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.97,0:21:37.10,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,It's right here, Umika.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.41,0:21:41.11,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,It lives inside you, sparkling brightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.11,0:21:44.20,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,The same goes for the promise \Nwe made back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.20,0:21:47.11,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,For you to take me to my home planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.11,0:21:48.75,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,Akeuchi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.54,0:21:54.90,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,The beacon of light inside you will \Nsurely show the way for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.90,0:21:56.56,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,Not just for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.56,0:22:00.01,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,I know that you'll help them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.01,0:22:03.41,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,You see, I've known it all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.41,0:22:07.36,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,After all, your feelings \Nare always what make me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.07,0:22:09.14,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,What make me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.14,0:22:11.14,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.14,0:22:12.25,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.25,0:22:14.07,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,I think I remember now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.07,0:22:15.14,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.14,0:22:17.37,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,A memory of my home planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.37,0:22:18.52,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.52,0:22:20.18,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,It's a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.18,0:22:21.63,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,Yes, a song!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.63,0:22:24.20,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,A song I sang often as a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.20,0:22:27.04,Default,Yu,0,0,0,,Just the one song, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.27,0:22:40.31,Narration,Umika,0,0,0,,It was like a flickering light.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.31,0:22:45.91,Narration,Umika,0,0,0,,A mysterious song, unfamiliar \Nyet nostalgic at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.69,0:22:48.35,Narration,Umika,0,0,0,,Unfettered and gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.35,0:22:50.00,Narration,Umika,0,0,0,,Powerful and unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.00,0:22:53.06,Narration,Umika,0,0,0,,A warm melody that \Nreminded me of Akeuchi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.28,0:22:56.85,Narration,Umika,0,0,0,,As though guided by her song,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.74,0:23:01.71,Narration,Umika,0,0,0,,I felt, with great certainty, \Nsomething shimmering within me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.48,0:23:04.77,Narration,Umika,0,0,0,,The courage given to me by Akeuchi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.77,0:23:06.55,Narration,Umika,0,0,0,,The courage given to me from everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.18,0:23:11.83,Narration,Umika,0,0,0,,A fierce hope inside me \Nto take the next step.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.83,0:23:15.00,Narration,Umika,0,0,0,,So these were my sparkles.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.62,0:23:18.13,Flashback,Yu,0,0,0,,I'm sure you know lots
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.13,0:23:20.37,Flashback,Yu,0,0,0,,about the wonderful things here on Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.49,0:23:26.38,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,Your planet must be a \Nwonderful place as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.10,0:23:29.13,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,Thank you, Akeuchi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.41,0:23:33.37,Default,Umika,0,0,0,,I was finally able to find it.
